| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4453 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3913a7a9-53a8-5db6-aea0-9f9ee5e620bc"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
